# Cloudflare Pages redirects. This file must live in the build output root
# that we have set up in the settings there, which is _build/html.
# So we keep it under docs/_extra, which Sphinx copies there via html_extra_path.
#
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>
#
# The limits are 2,100 redirects total. 2000 can be static, and a maximum of 100
# can be dynamic. We use roughly 29 rules, out of which 15 are dynamic.
#
# The rules are evaluated top to bottom and the first match wins. Cloudflare
# resolves static rules faster when they sit above any splat/placeholder lines,
# so all the exact-path rules come first, then the splat rules.
#
# About the archive destinations: the "web/3000/" prefix is an Internet Archive
# trick. There is no snapshot from the year 3000, so the Wayback Machine 302s to
# the closest capture, i.e., the most recent one. This always lands on the last
# archived version of the page instead of "web/*/", which shows a calendar list.
#

# Static rules for exact paths

# Rust Delhi x SciPy India meetup for August 2026
/sci-py-rs https://sci-py-rs.scipy.in 301

# Past editions that map to Internet Archive snapshots

/2009 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2009 301
/2010 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/scipyin/2010/ 301
/2011 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/scipyin/2011/ 301
/2012 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2012 301
/2013 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2013/ 301
/2014 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2014 301
/2015 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2015 301
/2016 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2016 301
/2017 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2017 301
/2018 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2018 301
/2019 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2019 301
/2020 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2020 301
/2021 https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2021 301

# Dynamic rules

/sci-py-rs/* https://sci-py-rs.scipy.in/:splat 301

/2009/* https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/2009/:splat 301
/2010/* https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/scipyin/2010/:splat 301
/2011/* https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/scipyin/2011/:splat 301
# 2010 and 2011 originally lived under /scipyin/<year>/. We catch those legacy links too.
/scipyin/* https://web.archive.org/web/3000/https://scipy.in/scipyin/:splat 301
